learning_outcomes.en:
Having passed this course of lectures a student
1. knows the basic notions of a parametrized curve and regular surface;
2. is able to find the velocity vector, acceleration vector, arc length,
curvature and torsion of a parametrized curve;
3. knows the notions of a natural parameter and the natural parametrization
of a curve and is able to find the natural parametrization of a curve;
4. knows the Frenet-Serret-Bartels equations and is able to use the method
of moving frame;
5. knows the notion of a vector field and is able to compute the covariant
derivative of a vector field;
6. knows the notion of a differential form in the three dimensional space
and is able to find the wedge product of differential forms and to calculate
the exterior differential of a differential form;
7. knows the notion of a shape operator and its properties;
8. is able to find the mean curvature, normal curvature and Gaussian
curvature of a surface;
9. recognizes the equation of a geodesic and is able to find the geodesics
on a surface;
10. knows the Gauss-Bonnet theorem and is able to find the Euler
characteristic of a surface.

learning_outcomes.et:
Selle kursuse läbinud üliõpilane:
1. teab parameetrilise joone ja regulaarse pinna mõisteid;
2. oskab leida joone kiirusvektorit, kiirendusvektorit, kaarepikkust,
kõverust ja väänet;
3. teab, mis on joone loomulik parameeter ja oskab leida joone
parameetrilist võrrandit, kui parameetriks on           loomulik parameeter;
4. teab Frenet-Setter-Bartelsi valemeid ja oskab kasutada liikuva reeperi
meetodit;
5. teab, mis on vektorväli ja oskab arvutada vektorvälja kovariantset
tuletist;
6. teab, mis on diferentsiaalvorm kolmemõõtmelises ruumis ja oskab arvutada
diferentsiaalvormide väliskorrutist ja välisdiferentsiaali;
7. teab, mis on Weingarteni operaator, ja selle omadusi;
8. oskab leida regulaarse pinna peakõverust, keskmist kõverust ja Gausi
kõverust;
9. teab geodeetilise joone võrrandit ja oskab leida geodeetilist joont
pinnal;
10. tunneb Gauss-Bonnet teoreemi ja oskab arvutada pinna Euleri
karakteristikut.
